{"tid":1780273,"cid":5,"subCid":12,"title":"[舊文回顧]  上海2020年要成為世界金融中心 這些缺點遭批差得遠","createTime":"2019-12-12T08:41:31.000Z","updateTime":"2019-12-12T16:02:46.000Z","uid":141151,"like":8,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":9,"replies":[{"pid":"f61c5e2360b83983ac3f52746e9140673586164d","tid":1780273,"uid":141151,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-12-12T08:41:31.000Z","msg":"上海2020年要成為世界金融中心 這些缺點遭批差得遠<br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://ec.ltn.com.tw/article/breakingnews/2748984\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fec.ltn.com.tw%2Farticle%2Fbreakingnews%2F2748984&d=Vh0AUGqI%2BhuKY3uG7C8Fc5ggdM0W6%2BkgeusliPwa7Y4%3D&h=7905f218\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=https%3A%2F%2Fec.ltn.com.tw%2Farticle%2Fbreakingnews%2F2748984&h=1abbad56\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://ec.ltn.com.tw/article/breakingnews/2748984</a><br />\n<br />\n〔財經頻道／綜合報導〕<strong><span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\"><span style=\"color: red;\">中國國務院10年前便已宣佈，要在2020年將上海建設為國際金融中心，但上海美國商會（AmCham Shanghai）今日最新報告指出，上海遠未達到全球金融中心的標準，人民幣兌換、網路限制、執照審批、法規不透明等都是阻礙。</span></span></strong><br />\n<br />\n為在明年達成此目標，今年1月中國8個監管部門共同發佈了1項行動準則，旨在將上海變為與倫敦或紐約相當的金融中心。<br />\n<br />\n但上海美國商會今日題為《2020年上海：一個達不到的金融願景》的報告訪問金融業內高層，大多數受訪者表示，與世界其他金融中心相比，在上海獲得執照非常困難，且審批過程中缺乏透明標準，這是最根本性的弱點。此外，人民幣仍然不是自由兌換貨幣，中國資本管制也幾乎沒有被鬆綁跡象。<br />\n<br />\n另外，部分受訪高層稱，他們還觀察到「窗口指導」（window guidance）的現象，也就是央行通過勸告和建議來影響商業銀行信貸，但此指導往往先通知中國銀行，使外國企業處於不利地位。報告便指出：「要得到國際金融中心的地位，先決條件之一便是國內外所有銀行得到平等對待。」<br />\n<br />\n報告最後指出，中國「網路長城」限制民眾使用谷歌或其他資訊來源，嚴重阻礙了上海的全球金融中心之路。"},{"pid":"04de24d832d3ba65091d9902601a98e6cb3f2c39","tid":1780273,"uid":48083,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-12-12T08:41:58.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"0e75507cbca6f99db5f6af5a53ed1e54cfcfda70","tid":1780273,"uid":124983,"like":10,"dislike":0,"score":10,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-12-12T08:43:53.000Z","msg":"仲有十幾日 上海就超越香港<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"dfa8497fece1623734411771afc928d24a17bb82","tid":1780273,"uid":141151,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"quote":{"pid":"0e75507cbca6f99db5f6af5a53ed1e54cfcfda70","tid":1780273,"uid":124983,"like":10,"dislike":0,"score":10,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-12-12T08:43:53.000Z","msg":"仲有十幾日 上海就超越香港<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-12-12T08:46:30.000Z","msg":"仲有十幾日  強国就全面建成小康社會<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"9990d57af0092725f83867087b917c900043fce2","tid":1780273,"uid":175346,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-12-12T08:51:04.000Z","msg":"此回覆已被刪除"},{"pid":"8daec8841b10f186014bc822d244e0178f2df968","tid":1780273,"uid":141151,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-12-12T09:14:09.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/hehe.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/hehe.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/hehe.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"414cd72b83e9c98c58945b21b446ac0f7a8ce72e","tid":1780273,"uid":154106,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-12-12T09:50:43.000Z","msg":"剩係法律方面有排都做唔到，起樓有咩易起姐？但法律唔保障私產權，又唔完善的話只會係三流金融中心。"},{"pid":"0e8ddbe23ec424490fc13a701455af81162e60a4","tid":1780273,"uid":141151,"like":0,"disli